				<td colspan="2"><span>The greaves and bp are decent stats.  There are better then greaves out there but they drop in KC so if there is a VS raid going then you may get lucky and get a chance at these.  The BP on the other hand just hope when you do your epic you get lucky and Trakabard drops it for you.  The 100hp heal is nice when you have taken a beating and don't feel like sitting for a while playing your song.  The only other SS I would suggest are the boots (clickie Aria of Eagle/2.5 min duration), the gloves (if don't have another perm eb item), helm (for scouting those see invis zones), and maybe bracer for the free DS/SvF.  Those last 2 are give or take but I love the lev on the boots as it hits the whole group and doesn't drop if they get to far away from you, just pay attention for the you are about to fall message.  You will get 2 before you drop.  Gloves are very nice EB item that is perm from lvl 1.</span></td>
